{"tid":427894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府09年提兩地兩檢可行 今變成不切實際","createTime":"2017-10-07T16:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T23:54:27.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61e3fa3cb933b8c6d0f4f8b0dcca9cb1a677ffb6","tid":427894,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"2009<br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/image1451263528525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2Fimage1451263528525.jpg&h=67e9ffc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府在2009年爭取立法會批出撥款興建高鐵時，時任運房局局長鄭汝樺曾講過，即使高鐵通車時未有一地兩檢，都可以有折衷方案，亦強調：「沒有『一地兩檢』不等於沒有高速。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017<br />\n陳帆「預告」立會發言　批民間方案無新意、不切實際<br />\n政府將於本月25日，在立法會提出在廣深港高鐵西九龍站實施「一地兩檢」無約束力議案，運輸及房屋局局長陳帆已率先向立法會提交當日發言「擬稿」，文中批評民間組織反建議在內地「一地兩檢」的方案，是無新意、不切實際、不合效益。"},{"pid":"dacc77299d0f966f71a5654ac2a334f2480c9247","tid":427894,"uid":26752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T18:40:10.000Z","msg":"高鐵=不切實際"},{"pid":"c508012792cac35cd43c4d003fe332612ffff2d9","tid":427894,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T18:43:16.000Z","msg":"支港融合新機遇<br />\n你識條鐵咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ad2daad8f26049a953fbdc764282ac23d40957","tid":427894,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T21:57:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d471542b015a1626f963d3ca73b157534908cf38","tid":427894,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T22:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下鄭汝樺之後去左邊間機構做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保守估計鄭汝樺轉會費高過尼馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b2ca1cbbabc27e35f5487fe3d185a9717ec6de","tid":427894,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07